name: The Dreaded Elevator (H&N 3)
description:
The elevator doors will open on the 19th January, 2022, 20:00pm UTC to reveal the location of Edition 4.

A future utility, as well as a bonus for both current H&N members and future members will also be revealed.

Directions: 
Click and move the mouse to look around (Full movement currently not supported on HEN)
Click on Elevator button to start it up. 

"If you die in an elevator, make sure you push the up button"
- Sam Levinson
